Value.value: A giant with a warm heart.
Hail! Hope you enjoy your stay here. We are growing again!
.. Say, do you maybe have a moment to assist me?
See, I'm ever on duty it seems, but I heard the shrine of Chauntea has lovely pink flowers!
Now, there is this girl I'm seeing and her favorite color is... well, pink. So I want to give her one of those flowers.
So could you get one for me? It's just north of here, and I would be very grateful if you could!
Have you got the flower yet? You can find them at the Shrine of Chauntea just north of here.
Thank you again! She loved the flower so much that she wants more of them *laughs*
Is that it? It sure is lovely! Thank you so much. Here! *hands over a small bag of coin*
